"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-07-29-Chinese-athletes-aim-for-track-and-field-medals-at-2024-Olympic-Games-1vD7uinamxa-p.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 145, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can change your cookie settings through your browser.\", \"from\": 146, \"to\": 203, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sports Scene  Copied  The track and field competitions at the 2024 Paris Summer Olympics will begin on Thursday.\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 317, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"China's team held a series of training sessions in Troyes, which is 180 kilometers away from the host city, to help some of its members get ready for the upcoming events.\", \"from\": 318, \"to\": 488, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 318, \"end\": 323, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9914384056585654, \"rank\": 0.004757894499011198, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 369, \"end\": 375, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ES_Troyes_AC\", \"score\": 0.6555040202509566, \"rank\": 0.5255046959172536, \"text\": \"Troyes\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ES_Troyes_AC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ES_Troyes_AC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Chinese triple jumper Zhu Yaming and sprinter Ge Manqi are both looking forward to standing on the podium in their competitions.\", \"from\": 490, \"to\": 618, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 490, \"end\": 497, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"score\": 0.9436190734968496, \"rank\": 0.056767951103391195, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"dbpedia\"